                <p>
                    <h4>
                        PREPARATION TIME OF THE CAPACITY REPORT
                    </h4>
                </p>

                <p>
                    After the firm has filled in the capacity request forms and applied, the appraisal committee assigned by the Industrial Services Unit conducts an inspection at the firm's workplace as soon as possible.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The reports prepared by evaluating the information and documents are sent to TOBB online for approval.
                </p>

                <p>
                    T.O.B.B. SUBMISSION OF CERTIFIED COPY FROM THE APPROVED CAPACITY REPORT
                </p>

                <p>
                    The capacity report prepared by the Adana Chamber of Industry is sent to the T.O.B.B. for approval after an agreement is reached with the company. The report returning from the approval is kept in Adana Chamber of Industry and when companies want to submit a capacity report to the relevant authorities, they can get a certified copy of this report.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Certification Price (changes in January of each year): 30 TL per page
                </p>

